okirikiri nt\u1ee5ziaka: Usoro CPU na-eso iji mezuo otu ntụziaka
superscalar architecture: Nhazi CPU nke nwere ike ime ọtụtụ ntuziaka kwa okirikiri elekere
am\u1ee5ma alaka: Usoro ebe CPU na-agbalị ịkọ ụzọ nke ọnọdụ ga-esi gaa
Northbridge: Chipset (sistemụ ochie) jikọtara CPU na RAM yana ụgbọ ala na-agba ọsọ
southbridge: Chipset (sistemụ ochie) nke jikwaa mpụta nwayọ nwayọ yana I/O
hyperthreading: Teknụzụ na-enye ohere ka otu isi CPU pụta dị ka ọtụtụ cores ezi uche dị na ya
risc: Tọọ Kọmputa ntụziaka belatara - imewe CPU nwere ntuziaka dị mfe
cisc: Ntụziaka dị mgbagwoju anya Tọọ Kọmputa - imewe CPU nwere ntuziaka siri ike ma dị mgbagwoju anya
simd: Otu Ntuziaka Otutu Data, Usoro maka nhazi data n'otu oge
microarchitecture: Nkọwapụta kpọmkwem mmejuputa iwu nke usoro ntụziaka CPU
usoro na mgbawa: Na-ejikọta ọtụtụ akụrụngwa (CPU, GPU, wdg) na otu mgbawa
agbakwunyere usoro: Sistemu kọmputa nke a raara nye otu ọrụ, na-abụkarị n'ime nnukwu ngwaọrụ
ngwa ngwa: Akụrụngwa echekwara na ngwaike kpamkpam (dị ka BIOS)
overclocking: Na-agba ọsọ CPU n'ọsọ dị elu karịa nkọwapụta ya
koodu mgbazi njehie: Usoro iji chọpụta na mezie mperi na RAM
n'usoro igbu: Usoro ebe CPU na-eme ntuziaka n'usoro dị mma karị
mgbak\u1ecd na mwep\u1ee5 quantum: Ụkpụrụ njide nke igwe ọrụ quantum maka mgbakọ
neuromorphic k\u1ecdmputa: Nrụmọrụ kọmpụta sitere n'ụbụrụ emebere maka ọrụ AI
